    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor usually says to be careful when sugars are low. if i take the full dose now when i barely ate anything, i'm pretty sure i'll just wake up with a massive hypo. isn't it safer to just skip the dose tonight since i'm already low and not eat much? it seems like the logical thing to do so i stay stable.",
